mg src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"486f2075d2cbd4cef1932aedf51e48b6affd2ff2","tid":630122,"uid":785,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T14:30:19.000Z","msg":"人地主動識我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上年去慕尼黑旅行，係安聯球場睇完波，<br />\n搭地鐵果陣，有4個德國腸走埋黎問我係邊度人...<br />\n傾傾下計，佢地又話N年前去過香港...<br />\n跟住佢地問我一唔一齊食晚飯，我又真係跟佢地去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n途中去左佢地其中一個屋企飲啤酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後佢地請我食飯...超級NICE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗起成個過程都幾痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28477c22155af47238f955a8acc9240c56035c1c","tid":630122,"uid":12973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"486f2075d2cbd4cef1932aedf51e48b6affd2ff2","tid":630122,"uid":785,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T14:30:19.000Z","msg":"人地主動識我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上年去慕尼黑旅行，係安聯球場睇完波，<br />\n搭地鐵果陣，有4個德國腸走埋黎問我係邊度人...<br />\n傾傾下計，佢地又話N年前去過香港...<br />\n跟住佢地問我一唔一齊食晚飯，我又真係跟佢地去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n途中去左佢地其中一個屋企飲啤酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後佢地請我食飯...超級NICE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗起成個過程都幾痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi